metadata.name: NYD #4727 Tribute Charm #1/8
metadata.description:
In true LMDesigns8 fashion I have created this tribute charm as an ode to this incredible NYD Queen!

My Ode to NYD #4727:

"That which is ugly in the eye of the beholder may only need to find the right light and audience for you to truly be seen!"

This AR Tribute Charm has a beautiful crystal backing that matches the truest hues of NYD #4727, she is a lover through and through and her heart chakra is vibrant!

🤩 Collect this piece to unlock unique AR experience 🤩

Original artwork done by Not Your Bro can be found here:  https://opensea.io/assets/ethereum/0x0fd1006fc15b1128514cfc9f25b16b6c9ee4fc80/4727

Huge Thanks to you all for:  
𝚂𝚞𝚙𝚙𝚘𝚛𝚝𝚒𝚗𝚐 𝙼𝚎𝚗𝚝𝚊𝚕 𝙷𝚎𝚊𝚕𝚝𝚑 🧠 & 𝙿𝚛𝚘𝚟𝚒𝚍𝚒𝚗𝚐 𝚄𝚝𝚒𝚕𝚒𝚝𝚢 𝚋𝚢 𝙽𝚘𝚝 𝚈𝚘𝚞𝚛 𝙱𝚛𝚘
